Effect - Class in model.weapons
This is an abstract class that is used to create four children: EffectDamage, EffectMark, EffectMoveYourself, EffectMoveTarget, in which it is implemented the abstract method Effect.executeEffect(Match, MoveController, ShootingParametersInput).
